<h2>New Student Added</h2>

<div class="alert alert-success">
  <strong>Great news!</strong> A new student has been added to your class.
</div>

<div class="student-card">
  <h3><%= @student.name %></h3>
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number"><%= @student.reading %></span>
      <span class="stat-label">Reading</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number"><%= @student.writing %></span>
      <span class="stat-label">Writing</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number"><%= @student.listening %></span>
      <span class="stat-label">Listening</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number"><%= @student.speaking %></span>
      <span class="stat-label">Speaking</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <p><strong>Total Score:</strong> <%= @student.total_score %>/40</p>
  <p><strong>Percentage:</strong> <%= @student.percentage.round(1) %>%</p>
  <p><strong>Added on:</strong> <%= @student.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></p>
</div>

<p>You can now start adding notes and tracking this student's progress. Click the button below to view their profile.</p>

<a href="<%= student_url(@student) %>" class="btn btn-success">View Student Profile</a>

<p>If you have any questions about this student or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact the system administrator.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
Student Records Management System</p>
